They are the dominant race in the rain forests and in the southern 
region of the world. Their skin is chocolate brown, and their eyes 
are emerald green. Their hair is straight with a bluish-black
color. Shaolu also have full lips and flattened noses. They spread 
into different tribes and villages all over the forests and southern 
great plains. Their culture is slightly different from one tribe to 
another, but they all hold certain beliefs in spirits and strange 
animal-gods. Shaolu are well-formed in both the magical arts and 
in the arts of war. They have a slightly bad reputation in
cities, being thieves and rogues. The average height of a Shaolu 
male is around 175 cm, and they weigh around 80 kgs. A normal 
Lifespan is around 80 years. 
